"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Israel said it stopped a missile, and Yemen's government blames Iran for pulling the country into the war. The world is focused on the Iran war, and there is uncertainty about what will happen next for Gaza.\",            \"english_title\": \"Israel Stops Missile\",            \"translated_version\": \"Israel dijo que par\u00f3 un misil, y el gobierno de Yemen culpa a Ir\u00e1n por meter al pa\u00eds en la guerra. El mundo est\u00e1 enfocado en la guerra de Ir\u00e1n, y hay incertidumbre sobre qu\u00e9 pasar\u00e1 despu\u00e9s con Gaza.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Israel Para Misil\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"One month into the conflict in Iran, Trump's approach is not working well.\",            \"english_title\": \"Trump's Approach Fails\",            \"translated_version\": \"Un mes en el conflicto en Ir\u00e1n, la forma de Trump no est\u00e1 funcionando bien.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Forma de Trump Falla\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The Israeli military confirms it killed Ali Shoeib from the Hezbollah-affiliated Al Manar TV.\",            \"english_title\": \"Israeli Military Action\",            \"translated_version\": \"El ej\u00e9rcito israel\u00ed confirma que mat\u00f3 a Ali Shoeib de la TV Al Manar afiliada a Hezbollah.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Acci\u00f3n Militar Israel\u00ed\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The craze for collecting ants surprises Kenya as smugglers try to make money.\",            \"english_title\": \"Ant Collecting Craze\",            \"translated_version\": \"La locura por coleccionar hormigas sorprende a Kenia mientras los contrabandistas intentan ganar dinero.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Locura por Hormigas\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Poor weather and lack of food and water led to deaths, says the Greek coastguard.\",            \"english_title\": \"Deaths Due to Weather\",            \"translated_version\": \"Mal clima y falta de comida y agua llevaron a muertes, dice la guardia costera griega.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Muertes por Clima\"        }    ]}"